{"tid":586412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英警確認前雙面諜中神經毒劑","createTime":"2018-03-09T13:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T14:37:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32d6fa5a7b4d676341b728936e2fe84b4a7f39f1","tid":586412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180309/20326411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326411&d=cPUuASb54NjB%2BpfASYGOkfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=04d1863b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326411&h=21612c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180309/20326411</a><br />\n<br />\n英警確認前雙面諜中神經毒劑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n俄羅斯前雙面間諜斯克里帕爾（Sergei Skripal）父女上周日在英國接觸不明物質後仍然昏迷垂危，警方高層前日確認「不明物質」為神經毒劑，案件列企圖謀殺案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180309/large/09wx05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180309%2Flarge%2F09wx05p.jpg&h=a80d538c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯克里帕爾遇襲前曾到便利店。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑毒氣藏禮物盒<br />\n<br />\n倫敦副警察局長勞利說：「本案是一宗重大事件，涉以神經毒劑企圖謀殺。」他相信行兇者是鎖定兩人施毒，但拒絕公佈神經毒劑種類及施毒手法。<br />\n<br />\n當局指，案中所用神經毒劑「非常罕見」，消息指不是VX或沙林毒氣，有指藏在斯克里帕爾女兒尤利亞（Yulia）朋友送的一盒禮物中，趁她由莫斯科飛到英國探父時借刀殺人，開箱放毒；這種毒劑全球只有幾個實驗室做得到，俄國情報科位於亞謝湼科實驗室是其一；亦有傳言說行兇者是出事當日將毒劑噴灑在二人臉上，或摻進他們午飯所喝的飲品中。<br />\n<br />\n內政大臣盧綺婷指，66歲的斯克里帕爾和33歲尤利亞情況依然危殆但穩定；此外，當時趕到現場的警員亦中毒留醫，但情況相對沒那麼嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/英國《太陽報》/《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"910584237e082e5d79060ab37096ee9a0d4552de","tid":586412,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c19472e2e3d650f8fc04c23186043436741180c","tid":586412,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"唔覺得係 putin 做<br />\nputin 要殺佢一早落手"},{"pid":"996d0cd6bc89257823b12bf688f3484e7fb3584f","tid":586412,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺得係 putin 做<br />\nputin 要殺佢一早落手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁KGB 做好多野都唔一定上報普京，即CIA 做野，侵侵唔會知。"},{"pid":"31d2988d7b83b0911089fd6a50d7ade1fd7069da","tid":586412,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cc88ec4e5128ad60d9fae26e04bc685f10de0b","tid":586412,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"996d0cd6bc89257823b12bf688f3484e7fb3584f","tid":586412,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺得係 putin 做<br />\nputin 要殺佢一早落手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁KGB 做好多野都唔一定上報普京，即CIA 做野，侵侵唔會知。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"殺一個已經變成平民既叛徒對俄有咩好處？"},{"pid":"bab760740f0550c5802aae1d94083bf67abc7f8b","tid":586412,"uid":5303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"67cc88ec4e5128ad60d9fae26e04bc685f10de0b","tid":586412,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"996d0cd6bc89257823b12bf688f3484e7fb3584f","tid":586412,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺得係 putin 做<br />\nputin 要殺佢一早落手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁KGB 做好多野都唔一定上報普京，即CIA 做野，侵侵唔會知。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"殺一個已經變成平民既叛徒對俄有咩好處？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好做叛徒"},{"pid":"fd2789a0aee6fdcb90c67698d1757fb617f2e9f0","tid":586412,"uid":79181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"67cc88ec4e51